{"tid":264293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ISS豪用4億公帑幫難民租房 業主經紀like爆：佢哋唔講價","createTime":"2017-05-30T16:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T06:28:58.000Z","uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f1e40fb1319e2b737ef388ddadd2e94ced3437","tid":264293,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"上周有傳媒踢爆，經香港國際社會服務社（ISS）派發給南亞裔難民的千二蚊超市食物券，被轉售給水貨集團圖利。ISS是唯一獲社署委託、援助難民的機構；獲得政府派錢，再以中介身份幫難民買食物、租樓。根據ISS去年的年報，組織四億二千九百萬的收入，其中四億一千一百萬來自政府。"},{"pid":"64d6f7db6bcd78a3d14781bfb28ea0c88dfbb748","tid":264293,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:54:55.000Z","msg":"以為ISIS"},{"pid":"a79c87bb01ee442a0d65a00b9c90f9a6e09167f9","tid":264293,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:56:06.000Z","msg":"咁就4億<br />\n我真係屌你老母"},{"pid":"1ad3bdf22fa6fe05265b4d855cbb28fa0223c198","tid":264293,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:01:54.000Z","msg":"4億渣？<br />\n比支那狗搶既千四億都唔止啦"},{"pid":"fcae289d6e99e8ccc4a0a9bc690de381282157a7","tid":264293,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatfat"},{"pid":"21b2d01995dfc4d1d28a1800c8b8f672d91d8638","tid":264293,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為ISIS</blockquote><br />\nMe too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f614968916db4f26b64bfcf9b66775366c72bd","tid":264293,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4億渣？<br />\n比支那狗搶既千四億都唔止啦</blockquote><br />\n根本南亞人係對抗支那蝗最佳武器，所以我係絕對支持佢地"},{"pid":"b266469143cc4d2d5a766e4675f3e19087e96ca2","tid":264293,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img